==Useful Info==
[[Smoke demon]]s are [[tier-3 demon]]s with dangerous ranged abilities. They are found in [[the Abyss]], [[Pandemonium]], and the [[Hell]]s, and they are often summoned by other monsters through the [[Summon Demon]] spell.

{{monster spells}}

==Tips & Tricks==
*Smoke demons are dangerous nuisances that will peg you with attacks as long as they're in your [[line of sight]]. Their Sticky Flame can deal fire damage when you're within 5 tiles of them, and their Smite deals irresistible, unavoidable damage. You can use the [[cloud]]s of steam created by their Steam Balls to give yourself some cover, fortunately.
*They have excellent resistance to fire damage and immunity to poison and negative energy, but otherwise their defenses are poor and they only have average HP.

==History==
{{CBA|0.31|smoke demons will have medium size.}}
*Prior to [[0.14]], they were a bit slower (speed 9).

[[Category:Demon]]
